Description: World of Warships 3D model export tools
 Command-line tools for exporting World of Warships ship geometry to glTF/GLB
 format. Includes wows-geometry-cli, wows-gltf-exporter, and wows-list-ships.

Package: libwows-geometry0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: World of Warships geometry parsing library
 Shared library for parsing World of Warships ship geometry data and
 exporting it to standard 3D formats.

Package: libwows-geometry-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
